{"tid":548763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"花生台遭PayPal凍結戶口","createTime":"2018-02-03T02:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T03:47:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"056bc1c12192527fea3537b192387e30a0dbf24c","tid":548763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180203/20294163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20294163&d=xIgoi0qI1Uh9wtwXt3H%2FzxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=368910dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20294163&h=d40bad72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180203/20294163</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n花生台遭PayPal凍結戶口 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180203/large/18163285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180203%2Flarge%2F18163285.jpg&h=ac466758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陶君行<br />\n<br />\n近年香港網台林立，除咗靠廣告維皮外，訂戶畀嘅月費都係其中一個主要收入，通常網台都用PayPal收月費，不過如果PayPal突然凍結個戶口，咁就大件事！最近陶君行就同八方呻，PayPal失驚無神凍結咗花生台戶口，除咗收唔到月費，連戶口入面嘅錢都拎唔到，最麻煩係PayPal到𠵱家都冇話畀佢聽，點先可以解凍。<br />\n<br />\n阿陶同八方講，之前收過PayPal電郵查詢，問佢係咪政治人物以及花生台生意模式。阿陶話佢只係一個喺網台開咪食花生嘅主持，點睇都唔係政治人物，所以咪照直講，點知都係俾PayPal凍結花生台個戶口，好多畀開月費嘅聽眾入唔到錢都好勞氣，而花生台亦用唔到戶口入面嘅錢畀日常開支，只好佢由自己出住先，但長此下去唔係辦法，希望PayPal快快講清楚點先可以解凍戶口。"},{"pid":"132f0aca0a3d29cb0e78a5425b47e48845c54f57","tid":548763,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"收ethereum/xmr"}]}